Description: These handcrafted burgers are smashed, seared and seasoned to order, using fresh, never frozen 100 percent Certified Angus Beef©. Whether you choose the Classic Smashburger or decide to create your own, the artisan buns, freshly chopped produce, flavorful sauces and variety of cheeses are designed to deliver a great-tasting, juicy burger you can taste in every bite.
Location: 3500 Las Vegas Blvd. South Las Vegas, 89109

Description: Here, the ultimate Las Vegas sandwich is much more than just meat between two slices of bread. The extensive menu brings sandwiches to a whole new artistic level, each made with fresh-baked, artisan bread and the finest ingredients.

Description: Perfect for any time of the day, Crepes and More offers a variety of sweet and savory crepes. The menu also includes sweets and treats, such as ice cream sundaes, bagels, croissants, parfaits, and fruit. Complete your meal with a specialty coffee by Intelligentsia or gourmet tea by Forte.
Location: 3500 Las Vegas Blvd. South Las Vegas, 89109

Description: Perfect for lunch, dinner or evening cravings, The Halal Guys is open late into the night to cater to night owls looking for a post-OMNIA Nightclub bite. The menu features signature sandwiches and platters with a choice of chicken, beef gyro, chicken and gyro combo or crispy falafel- all seasoned to perfection. Meals are made to be customized with toppings like smooth hummus, smoky baba ghanoush, golden fries, white sauce, or fiery hot sauce.ÿ
Location: 3500 Las Vegas Blvd. South Las Vegas, 89109
